'''史蒂芬·沙森'''（{{lang-en|'''Steven J. Sasson'''}}，{{bd|1950年|7月4日|||}}），[[美國|美國]][[電機工程師|電機工程師]]，[[數位相機|數位相機]]的發明人<ref name="The Rediff Interview/Steven J Sasson, inventor of the digital camera">{{cite web|title=The Rediff Interview/Steven J Sasson, inventor of the digital camera|url=http://www.rediff.com/money/2006/aug/07kodak.htm|publisher=Rediff.com India Limited|accessdate=22 September 2011|date=August 7, 2006|archive-date=2015-02-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150211010305/http://www.rediff.com/money/2006/aug/07kodak.htm|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

==學經歷==
沙森生於[[紐約市|紐約市]][[布鲁克林区|布鲁克林区]]，雙親是 Ragnhild Tomine 和 John Vincent Sasson，母親是[[挪威|挪威]]人<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://rogaland-historie.no/SydvestenPdf/Sydvesten%202008-1.pdf |title=NORSKAMERIKANEREN BAK DIGITALKAMERAET |access-date=2015-02-04 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160303235203/http://rogaland-historie.no/SydvestenPdf/Sydvesten%202008-1.pdf |archive-date=2016-03-03 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>。沙森先後於1972和1973年獲得[[壬色列理工學院|壬色列理工學院]][[電機工程|電機工程]][[學士|學士]]和[[碩士|碩士]]學位<ref name="The Rediff Interview/Steven J Sasson, inventor of the digital camera"/>。他的發明開始於1975年在[[伊士曼柯達公司|伊士曼柯達公司]]，當時他的上級加雷斯·A·勞埃德（Gareth A. Lloyd）計劃使用[[感光耦合元件|感光耦合元件]]（CCD）製作一台電子式照相機<ref name=ap>Dobbin, Ben. (2005-09-08)  [http://www.seattlepi.com/business/article/Kodak-engineer-had-revolutionary-idea-the-first-1182624.php Kodak ] {{Wayback|url=http://www.seattlepi.com/business/article/Kodak-engineer-had-revolutionary-idea-the-first-1182624.php |date=20141129040439 }}. seattlepi.com. Retrieved on 2011-11-15.</ref>。沙森今日在柯達公司負責保護該公司的[[智慧資本|智慧資本]]<ref name=ap />。

==第一台數位相機==
沙森於1975年在柯達公司發明第一台數位相機，該相機重量3.6公斤，拍攝影像只有1萬[[像素|像素]]，所拍攝影像被記錄在[[卡式录音带|卡式录音带]]內，記錄每幅影像過程花費23秒，拍攝的影像為黑白影像<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.thedonutproject.com/inspiration/inventor-of-the-digital-camera/ |title=Steven Sasson, Inventor of the Digital Camera |accessdate=2015-02-04 |archive-date=2015-02-11 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150211003614/http://www.thedonutproject.com/inspiration/inventor-of-the-digital-camera/ |dead-url=yes }}</ref>。當沙森開始這項電子相機開發計畫時，他預想未來的相機將是沒有機械運動部件的<ref>{{YouTube|RGoCL1F-xVw}}</ref>。該數位相機獲得{{US patent|4131919}}。

==榮譽與獎項==
2010年，[[徠卡相機|徠卡相機]]在該年[[世界影像博覽會|世界影像博覽會]]（Photokina）上，將徠卡生產的第400萬台數位相機——一台1800萬畫素的{{link-en|徠卡 M9|Leica M9}}鈦金限量版數位相機贈與沙森，作為對他的[[致敬|致敬]]<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://pdnonline.com/gear/Photokina-2010-Day-0-388.shtml |title=Photokina 2010 Day 0: Leica Drives a VW; 20-Foot Chase Jarvis; Canons Along The Rhine - See more at: http://pdnonline.com/gear/Photokina-2010-Day-0-388.shtml#sthash.Srx8iXX5.dpuf |accessdate=2015-02-04 |archive-date=2015-02-04 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150204183629/http://pdnonline.com/gear/Photokina-2010-Day-0-388.shtml |dead-url=yes }}</ref>。2010年11月17日，[[美國總統|美國總統]][[贝拉克·奥巴马|贝拉克·奥巴马]]在[[白宮|白宮]]{{link-en|白宮東房|East Room|東房}}授予沙森{{link-en|美國國家科技創新獎章|National Medal of Technology and Innovation}}<ref name="Whitehouse">{{cite web|url=http://www.whitehouse.gov/blog/2010/11/18/president-obama-awards-national-medals-science-technology-and-innovation|title=President Obama Awards National Medals of Science, Technology and Innovation|date=18 November 2010|work=whitehouse.gov|accessdate=2015-02-04|archive-date=2015-03-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150302071203/http://www.whitehouse.gov/blog/2010/11/18/president-obama-awards-national-medals-science-technology-and-innovation|dead-url=no}}</ref>，這是[[美國政府|美國政府]]授予科學家、工程師與發明家的最高獎項<ref name="National Medal of Technology and Innovation">{{cite web|url=http://www.whitehouse.gov/blog/2010/11/17/what-you-missed-tuesday-talk-national-medals-laureates-science-technology-and-innova|title=What You Missed: Tuesday Talk on The National Medals Laureates of Science, Technology and Innovation|date=17 November 2010|work=whitehouse.gov|accessdate=2015-02-04|archive-date=2015-02-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150216040920/http://www.whitehouse.gov/blog/2010/11/17/what-you-missed-tuesday-talk-national-medals-laureates-science-technology-and-innova|dead-url=no}}</ref>。2012年9月6日，{{link-en|英國皇家攝影學會|Royal Photographic Society}}授予沙森進步獎章，並且沙森成為該會榮譽會士，以表彰他的發明、研究、出版或其他使攝影與成像科學技術廣泛地有重大進步貢獻<ref>[http://www.ephotozine.com/article/royal-photographic-society-awards-winners-20062 Royal Photographic Society Awards Winners] {{Wayback|url=http://www.ephotozine.com/article/royal-photographic-society-awards-winners-20062 |date=20150204200103 }}[http://www.rps.org/awards/history/progress-medal Progress Medal, Royal Photographic Society] {{Wayback|url=http://www.rps.org/awards/history/progress-medal |date=20150204193835 }}</ref>。

